#include<iostream>
#include<cstdlib>
using namespace std;

typedef unsigned long long INT;

int main(void)
{
	INT a, b, count;
	INT F1, F2, temp;
	
	while(1)
	{
		scanf("%llu %llu",&a, &b);
		if(!a)
		{
			if(!b)
			{
				break;
			}
		}
		
		count=0;
		F1=1;
		F2=2;
		
		while(F2<=b)
		{
			temp=F1+F2;
			F1=F2;
			F2=temp;
			
			if(F1>=a)
			{
				count++;
			}
		}
		
		printf("%llu\n",count);
	}
	
	return 0;
}
